        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 1. A, Calcinus elegans (H. Milne Edwards, 1836). Male SL 10.0 mm, stn M1; B, Calcinus fuscus Malay, Komai & Chan, 2012. Male SL 4.1 mm, stn B42; C, Calcinus gaimardii (H. Milne Edwards, 1848). Female SL 5.6 mm, stn R14; D, Calcinus laevimanus (Randall, 1840). Male SL 4.4 mm, stn M2; E, Calcinus latens (Randall, 1840). Male SL 3.0 mm, stn R1; F, Calcinus lineapropodus Morgan & Forest, 1991. Male SL 4.5 mm, stn R16; G, Calcinus minutus Buitendijk, 1937. Male SL 4.7 mm, stn R10; H, Calcinus morgani Rahayu & Forest, 1999. Female ovig SL 4.8 mm, stn M2." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4503030/files/figure.png" .

